OL,3,C'We're open for the football' pub
OL,4,Ctells punters after landlady shot
OL,6,FA pub has told punters "of course
OL,7,Fwe're open" for England's Euro 2024
OL,8,Fsemi-final less than two weeks after
OL,9,Fits landlady was shot.
OL,11,FBonita Page, who runs The Red Lion, in
OL,12,FWath upon Dearne, near Rotherham, said
OL,13,Fshe had put her "big knickers on"
OL,14,Fafter she suffered serious leg
OL,15,Finjuries in the incident.
OL,17,FMs Page, 55, was shot outside the pub
OL,18,Fon High Street when a group of men
OL,19,Fturned up on 28 June.
