OL,3,C'We're open for the football' pub
OL,4,Ctells punters after landlady shot
OL,6,FIn a post on Facebook, the pub said it
OL,7,Fwas business as usual as England
OL,8,Fprepare to face Netherlands in
OL,9,FWednesday's semi-final.
OL,11,FIt said: "Yes of course we're open
OL,12,FWednesday for England."
OL,14,FMs Page, 55, wrote that "normal
OL,15,Fservices" had resumed.
OL,17,F'Recovery starts here'
