OL,3,C'We're open for the football' pub
OL,4,Ctells punters after landlady shot
OL,6,FShe added: "Bring your flags, banners,
OL,7,Fclappers. Come make some noise,
OL,8,Fsupport your country. Leave drama at
OL,9,Fthe door."
OL,11,FShe said there would be security on
OL,12,Fthe door.
OL,14,FIt is thought several men were in the
OL,15,Farea at the time of the shooting. The
OL,16,Farea outside the pub in High Street
OL,17,Fwas cordoned off and evidence of a
OL,18,Fshooting was found at the scene.
