OL,3,C'We're open for the football' pub
OL,4,Ctells punters after landlady shot
OL,6,FIn an earlier post Ms Page offered a
OL,7,F"massive thank you to my family and
OL,8,Ffriends and staff for being by my side
OL,9,Fcontinuously since the madness".
OL,11,F"Recovery starts here," she said.
OL,13,FShe said she had needed "several
OL,14,Fhospital appointments each week" and
OL,15,Fit had been "a rough 10 days".
OL,17,F"But big knickers on and the amazing
OL,18,Fsupport from family and friends, we
OL,19,Fwill be fine," she said.
